This is version 0.90 of the PDL::NDF module
-------------------------------------------

This module allows NDF files to be written and read from PDL.
All numerical array components are read as PDLs.

Information on using this module is available in PDL::NDF.pm

Requirements:
------------

This package has been tested with PDL-1.03. It will not work with more
recent alpha versions.

You will also need the NDF module (which should be part of this
distribution).

Installation
------------

To install this package independently of the main package type:

perl Makefile.PL
make
make install



